column5: HAPPY NEW YEAR to all my friends and family on OFC. May 2017 be the best for all
All the best in the new year and my the fish gods bring everyone a great year on and off the water
Here's to good health and personal bests in 2017!
All the Best to you All in 2017...

All the best to all for 2017. Beans I wish I did the same thing! I spent it with my 4 kids and 8 grands and friends but we suffered from the loud venue music and crowded And it wasn't cheap!!!! Live and learn!
Happy New Year to you & your family!
Happy New Kelvin and all on OFC, may 2017 bring more Fishies in the boat for you.
